data.description: Charming townhome in Horseshoe Park! Featuring 2 beds, 1.5 baths, with a family room, dining area and a modern kitchen on the main floor. The updated kitchen boasts updated cabinets, countertops and newer appliances. Enjoy the outdoors on the patio with additional storage. The main bedroom offers an extra sink/vanity and dual closets. Laminate flooring throughout and recent exterior paint to add a fresh touch.
